id: "class:bard#dirge_bard"
name: "Dirge Bard"
description: "A composer of sonorous laments for the dead and elaborate requiems for\
  \ those lost yet long remembered, dirge bards master musical tools and tropes that\
  \ must appeal to the ears and hearts of both the living and the dead."
